lied low compressibiity\ncondition, viscous GASPHER model shows clear spiral pattern profiles\ndemonstrating the better quality of results compared to SPH viscous ones.\nMoreover a successful comparison of results concerning GASPHER 1D inviscid\nshock tube with analytical solution is also reported.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Jun 2010 16:09:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Jun 2010 14:49:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 11 Jun 2010 10:18:52 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 21 Jun 2010 08:57:49 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 2010 06:15:26 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Sat, 20 Aug 2011 09:15:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
